channel.title: Dicing
channel.description: Don't listen to anything casey says. Dicing will lose you money. People are assholes and will always scam you in the long run. Do not listen to any of them. Don't bother with any of that shit, it's fucking stupid and it makes you broke. People say "trusted this" "trusted that". It's all bullfuck. They even offer to show you a cash stack. Where do you think they got that cash? Scamming. Never dice, it's complete bullshit, and it fucks over the economy of this game. I just got scammed by 2 people, the second coming up and telling me not to worry, I have all this money, and santas, etc. It's all complete bullshit. I'm tired of it. Dice were the shittiest item ever added.
